File System Operations:
- Create, read, update, delete files and directories
- Manage file permissions and ownership
- Support for hidden files and dotfiles
- Wildcard expansion and pattern matching
- Path resolution (absolute, relative, ~, .., .)

Process Management:
- Track running processes with realistic PIDs
- Background job execution and control
- Process signals and termination
- CPU and memory usage simulation

Package Management:
- Install and remove packages
- Dependency resolution
- Package search and information display
- Package cache management

Network Operations:
- Web search via browser command
- File downloads with curl/wget
- Network diagnostics (ping, netstat, ifconfig)
- DNS resolution simulation

Text Editing:
- Full nano editor simulation with controls
- Vim editor with modes and commands
- Command-line text manipulation (sed, awk, grep)

Programming Support:
- Python3 interpreter and script execution
- Git version control operations
- Script execution and compilation
- Development tool integration

System Information:
- Real-time system stats (/proc filesystem)
- Disk usage and memory information
- User and permission management
- Environment variable handling

Advanced Features:
- Command history tracking
- Environment variable persistence
- Alias creation and management
- Job control (fg, bg, jobs)
- Command substitution
- Shell scripting support
